Ing '''Leying Godwin''' (a king Ingles ausan dang ''Godwin's law'', ''Godwin's Rule of Nazi Analogies'' o ''Godwin's Law of Nazi Analogies''<ref name="GL FAQ">{{cite web|author=Tim Skirvin |title=How to post about Nazis and get away with it—the Godwin's law FAQ|url= http://www.faqs.org/faqs/usenet/legends/godwin/ |date=1999-2009 |work=Skirv's Wiki |accessdate=2006-05-07}}</ref><ref name="Godwin94">{{cite news|author=[[Mike Godwin|Godwin, Mike]]|title=Meme, Counter-meme|date=October, 1994|work=[[Wired magazine|Wired]]|url= http://www.wired.com/wired/archive/2.10/godwin.if_pr.html |accessdate=2006-03-24}}</ref>) metung yang argumentu o pamangaintuliran a gewa nang [[Mike Godwin]] anyang 1990<ref name="Godwin94" />{{Primary source-inline|date=August 2012}} a megi nang [[Internet humor|kasebyan king Aptas]] (''Internet adage'') . Sasabian nang "Kuntoru kakaba ing pisasabyan, alus siguradung daragul ing posibilidad a pakiyanti ya iti o ikumpara kareng [[Nazi Party|Nazi]] o kang  [[Adolf Hitler|Hitler]]." ("As an online discussion grows longer, the probability of a comparison involving [[Nazi Party|Nazis]] or [[Adolf Hitler|Hitler]] [[Limit (mathematics)|approaches]] [[almost surely|1]].")<ref name="Godwin94"/><ref name="Godwin95canonical version">{{cite web| author=[[Mike Godwin|Godwin, Mike]] | title=Godwin's law of Nazi Analogies (and Corollaries)|publisher=[[Electronic Frontier Foundation]]|date=January 12, 1995 | work=EFF.org|pages="Net Culture – Humor" archive section|url= http://w2.eff.org/Net_culture/Folklore/Humor/godwins.law |accessdate=2012-06-19}}</ref> King makuyad a salita, apansinan na apagumasdan Godwin a, nung mika ustung panaun, sanumang pamisabi-sabi o diskusyun king [[Aptas]] panibatan ne ning pamiyanti o pamagkumpara kang Hitler ampo kareng Nazi.

Maralas, gagamitan de ing Leying Godwin antimong pamagpigil kareng argumentu king maleparan a pormang ''[[Reductio ad Hitlerum]]''.{{citation needed|date=August 2012}} Ing ''Reductio ad Hitlerum'' pagtangkan neng sambutan ing argumentu uling iti ginamit ne o dela neng Hitler.<ref>{{cite book|last=Strauss|first=Leo|title=Natural Right and History|year=1953|publisher=University of Chicago Press|location=Chicago, Il.|isbn=0-226-77692-1|link=http://books.google.com/books?id=LT1V8Xgz1EUC|pages=42–3}}</ref> Ala yang sasabyan ing patakaran o leyi nung bage ya ing pangabanggit o pamagkumpara kang [[Adolf Hitler]] o deng [[Nazism|Nazi]], sasabyan na mung malyaring marapat iti, king lambatan ning diskusyun, bage ya man o ali. Uli na niti, sasabyan nang   Godwin a kailangang lisyan ing pamanabusu o sobrang pamangamit kareng pamagkumparang deti kareng Nazi o kang Hitler, uling lalako na da ing epektu da reng makatud o matulid a pamagkumpara o pamiyanti.<ref name="CRDFSDA">''[[Cyber Rights: Defending Free Speech in the Digital Age]]''</ref>

Lipat ning king metung kareng mumuna nang uri o porma ning leying Godwin makaturu yang partikular kareng diskusyun kareng [[Usenet]] [[newsgroup]], ref name="Godwin 1991">{{cite newsgroup|author=[[Mike Godwin|Godwin, Mike]]|title=Re: Nazis (was Re: Card's Article on Homosexuality|date=August 18, 1991|newsgroup=rec.arts.sf-lovers|id=1991Aug18.215029.19421@eff.org|url= http://groups.google.com/groups?selm=1991Aug18.215029.19421%40eff.org}}</ref> gagamitan de ngeni ing leyi king sanumang [[Conversation threading|threaded online discussion]], kayabe la reng kareng [[Internet forum|forum]], [[chat room]] ampong [[blog]] comment thread, at mababanggit ya king e bageng pamagkumpara o pamiyanting Nazi kareng artikulu o talumpati o speech.<ref name="Goldacre 2010">{{cite web|title=Pope aligns atheists with Nazis. Bizarre. Transcript here. |url= http://bengoldacre.posterous.com/nazi-youth-pope-aligns-atheists-with-nazis-bi |author=Ben Goldacre|publisher=bengoldacre - secondary blog
